overview: What’s the outcome of mixing beauty, sensuality, desire and ambition? ...SEX! During the shooting of Shakespeare’s classic, the whole team let themselves be pulled by the erotism and free-will of their desires. In this issue of PRIVATE’s sexual diary, the director, actresses, make-up artists and assistants get involved in a sexual adventure to satisfy their desires, as well as their ambitions
title: Amanda's Diary 5
